/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340290/extras/fb86e33ddc8585bb594f9c297a27133c.webm?t=1706659006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340290/extras/fb86e33ddc8585bb594f9c297a27133c.mp4?t=1706659006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><br>· Simple operation, fun adventure.<br><br>· Exquisite level design, each level is hand-drawn.<br><br>· Support all popular game handles, without any settings, just connect the handles.<br><br>· Exquisite game screen, players will cross to various styles of dungeons in the game.<br><br>· Good game soundtrack.",
